                <div class="container">
                    <div class="contact-strip reveal">
                        <div class="contact-text">
                            <h2>Got Questions?<br>Let's <span style="color:var(--red)">Talk.</span></h2>
                            <p>We'd love to hear from enthusiasts, partners, or anyone who has feedback.</p>
